channel.title: Wtf? What happened?
channel.description:
Ok, my servers have been running since 2007. Everything hosting-wise has been fine, until about 30 mins ago. My server had people on, it restarted (like usual) and al of a sudden no1 could connect. I double checked my port forwarding, redirects, everything, but it just stopped hosting. I restarted the server a few times and nothing...
I then tried connecting with 127.0.0.1 and it worked. I tried with my ##.###.###.### (whatsmyip.org) address as well, which didnt worked. So I think it is my portforwarding. But I didnt change it...
